text: David Noonan (8 January 1876 - 10 March 1929) was an Australian cricketer. He played five first-class matches for New South Wales in 1895/96. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1876 births Category:1929 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
